traxx is a 1988 action/adventure comedy film that was directed by jerome gary . it released on august 17 , 1988 and starred shadoe stevens as a mercenary turned cookie maker . the film had a budget of 6.5 million dollars and was initially intended to have a theatrical release , but was instead released direct to video . traxx was later screened in 2012 at the hollywood theatre in portland , oregon . a handful of middle-aged males from texas ( at least two ) consider traxx to be one of the greatest films ever made .